title: Rollin' With The Chromies Linear Holographic Nail Polish- 0.5 oz Full Sized Bottle
description:
Similar in shift to Shade Shifter, this multi-chrome also has a linear holo! This polish changes from cyan, to blue, to red orange, to burgundy, and more.  I most often see a cyan blue shade. Best in 3 coats, or 1 coat over black, this polish is one you will have to see to believe!

Type: Multi-Chrome w/Linear Holo
